title: QnA with Pandas Dataframe
author: Shivam Patel
description: This Streamlit app allows you to perform question answering on a pandas DataFrame loaded from an Excel or CSV file.

installDependencyCommands: pip install streamlit==1.34.0 pandas==2.1.4 numpy==1.26.4 ibm_watson_machine_learning==1.0.356 python-dotenv langchain==0.2.1 langchain_experimental==0.0.59
